	<p>Sentree was a new IoT device that opens the market for managed home and commercial HVAC systems. Contractors install the device and can receive alerts when there's a problem. </p>

	<p>The initial site at <a href="http://www.sentree.com">sentree.com</a> was meant to answer initial questions that an HVAC contractor would have about how the system worked. The goal was to capture contact information for follow-up demos. </p>

