	<p>The client wanted a short deadline and asked that it be created with the X-Theme wordpress platform. That was my first time using X-Theme and although the appeal of it is obvious, I realized immediately that this is not for me.</p>

	<p>I learned web standards-based development, and this seems like a complete regression both in terms of process and actual code quality. All primary element styles can be applied through the Wordpress interface, which means that all of it gets added inline to each element.</p>

